                                A student with many skills is always advantageous and web development helps you to gain
                                programming skills in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, etc., designing skills, SEO skills, and a
                                lot more.
                                Most importantly it helps you to build upon your resume helping you to have good
                                prospects in the job. It is not just a single skill but a cluster of many skills which a
                                student can develop.

                            </p>
